If you want to talk im here for you... 
But if you cant go without selfharm, its better when youre drunk then you wont feel the pain

Thank you.. she really didnt took it well. After i woke up she stayed with me as long as she could but always cried. I dont have a good realtionship with my parents so they came over and acted all caring but left my room soon after that 
My sister is really all i have left now
Hey.. pretty fucked up myself. You can dm me if u want help or just someone to talk to
